{"sections":{"breadcrumbs_DgnWDV":{"type":"breadcrumbs","settings":{"container":"fixed","text_alignment":"start","padding_top":16,"padding_bottom":20}},"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{"container":"fixed","text_alignment":"center","padding_top":28,"padding_bottom":28}},"custom_liquid_TBBFFm":{"type":"custom-liquid","name":"t:sections.custom-liquid.name","settings":{"custom_liquid":"<center><iframe width=\"660\" height=\"380\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/g0LB4op4PQs?si=xe35y312dDcM2Du4\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe><\/center>","color_scheme":"","padding_top":50,"padding_bottom":0}},"rich_text_kyFd96":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_Y9MMVQ":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"About","highlight_style":"none","highlight_font_style":"italic","highlight_style_color":"","highlight_text_color":"","heading_size":"h2"}},"text_7h6LaE":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Located in the Midwest near the Twin Cities, Ball Pro has been a leader in the advertising specialty industry since 1992. We proudly specialize in providing promotional solutions across golf, apparel, sports, and home categories, all while continuously enhancing our in-house print capabilities to meet the evolving needs of our customers. Exceptional customer service is the foundation of our company, and our mission is to simplify your work as a distributor by offering quality products, knowledgeable staff, and brilliant imprints.<\/p><p>Our growth journey reflects our commitment to diversifying our product range. In 2017, we acquired Diversified Ad-Tee and rebranded it as Diversified Quality Kitchenware, broadening our selection with kitchen and drinkware products. In 2023, we entered the apparel market by acquiring Logo Sport, adding high-quality branded clothing to our offerings. To expand our apparel capabilities even further, we acquired Branded Apparel in early 2025. That same year, we consolidated all our brands under Ball Pro, establishing ourselves as a trusted supplier for all your golf, apparel, sports, and home promotional needs. We also moved from Eden Prairie to a larger facility in Golden Valley, more than doubling our production space.<\/p><p>At Ball Pro, we offer comprehensive solutions that extend beyond simple products. Whether you need a unique accessory, a custom kit, or a fully integrated promotional campaign, our in-house experts are ready to provide innovative ideas tailored to your needs. Thank you for visiting our website—we look forward to the opportunity to serve you and help make your next promotional project a resounding success.<\/p>","text_size":"text-base","text_line_limit":"none","button_style":"btn--underline","button_icon":"none"}}},"block_order":["heading_Y9MMVQ","text_7h6LaE"],"custom_css":[".rich-text {max-width: 78rem; margin: 0 auto;}","@media (max-width: 1023px) {.rich-text__heading {max-width: 50rem; margin: 0 auto; }}"],"settings":{"container":"fixed","color_scheme":"","use_color_scheme_in_container":false,"content_spacing":"standard","content_alignment":"center","padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":100,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"fixed"}},"multicolumn_NVWxEe":{"type":"multicolumn","blocks":{"column_gnmDqV":{"type":"column","settings":{"title":"Nicootitto","highlight_style":"none","highlight_font_style":"italic","highlight_style_color":"","highlight_text_color":"","heading_size":"h4","text":"<p>Founder\/CEO<\/p>","text_size":"text-base","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_style":"btn--underline","button_icon":"none"}},"column_Lkgb3Y":{"type":"column","settings":{"title":"Jake Nakos","highlight_style":"none","highlight_font_style":"italic","highlight_style_color":"","highlight_text_color":"","heading_size":"h4","text":"<p>Designer<\/p>","text_size":"text-bas